    "text_english": "Just as a lamp in a windless place does not flicker, so the disciplined yogi, ever devoted, reaches Me.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
  },
  {
    "parva_number": 6,
    "chapter": 9,
    "verse": 15,
    "text_sanskrit": "अन्नदात्तास्सर्वभूतानां यो मद्भक्तः स मे प्रियः | भक्‍तेनैव निवेद्यते स सुखं विन्दति चिरम् ||",
    "text_transliteration": "annadattās sarvabhūtānāṃ yo madbhaktaḥ sa me priyaḥ | bhaktenaiva nivedyate sa sukhaṃ vindati ciram ||",
    "text_english": "He who offers sustenance to all beings as My devotee is dear to Me; by devotion alone, he attains lasting happiness.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
  },
  {
    "parva_number": 6,
    "chapter": 9,
    "verse": 16,
    "text_sanskrit": "यो मां प्रभlति सर्वेषु भूतेषु च | भगवन् तं तं मद्भक्तं सदा सुखं लभते ||",
    "text_transliteration": "yo māṃ prabhlati sarveṣu bhūteṣu ca | bhagavan taṃ taṃ madbhaktaṃ sadā sukhaṃ labhate ||",
    "text_english": "Whoever worships Me with devotion, seeing Me in all beings, he attains eternal bliss.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
  },
  {
    "parva_number": 6,
    "chapter": 9,
    "verse": 17,
    "text_sanskrit": "यदस्मिन् भूतानामात्मा नित्यमवस्थितः | तस्मात्सर्वेषु भूतानुयोगिनो भवति ||",
    "text_transliteration": "yad asmin bhūtānām ātmā nityam avasthitaḥ | tasmāt sarveṣu bhūtānuyogino bhavati ||",
    "text_english": "The self is ever present in all beings; thus, the yogi, recognizing this, sees all beings in Me.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
  },
  {
    "parva_number": 6,
    "chapter": 9,
    "verse": 18,
    "text_sanskrit": "अनन्यभक्तिर्भवेत्सर्वेषु भूतेषु च | मयि सर्वाणि कर्माणि समर्पयन् स मयि च ||",
    "text_transliteration": "ananya‑bhaktir bhavet sarveṣu bhūteṣu ca | mayi sarvāṇi karmāṇi samarpayan sa mayi ca ||",
    "text_english": "Exclusive devotion arises when one surrenders all actions to Me, seeing Me in all beings.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
  },
  {
    "parva_number": 6,
    "chapter": 9,
    "verse": 19,
    "text_sanskrit": "सर्वधर्मान्परित्यज्य मामेकं शरणं व्रज | अहं त्वां सर्वपापेभ्यो मोक्षयिष्यामि मा शुच: ||",
    "text_transliteration": "sarva‑dharmān parityajya mām ekaṃ śaraṇaṃ vraja | ahaṃ tvāṃ sarva‑pāpebhyo mokṣayiṣyāmi mā śucḥ ||",
    "text_english": "Abandon all dharmas and take refuge in Me alone; I will free you from all sins. Do not grieve.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
  },
  {
    "parva_number": 6,
    "chapter": 9,
    "verse": 20,
    "text_sanskrit": "यस्त्वात्मा सर्वभूतानि मां विद्धि सर्वभूतान् | तत्सर्वाणि भूतानि तेनैव मोक्ष्यन्ति च ||",
    "text_transliteration": "yastv ātmā sarva‑bhūtāni māṃ viddhi sarva‑bhūtān | tat sarvāṇi bhūtāni tenaiva mokṣyanti ca ||",
    "text_english": "He who sees Me as the self of all beings, all beings are freed by him.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
  },
  {
    "parva_number": 6,
    "chapter": 9,
    "verse": 21,
    "text_sanskrit": "मन्मे यः भक्त्या नित्यं युक्त: कर्म करोति सः | मयि तस्य मनःस्थितः सदा भवति ||",
    "text_transliteration": "manme yaḥ bhaktyā nityaṃ yuktaḥ karma karoti saḥ | mayi tasya manaḥ sthitaḥ sadā bhavati ||",
    "text_english": "Whoever constantly acts with devotion, and whose mind is fixed on Me, abides in Me always.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
  },
  {
    "parva_number": 6,
    "chapter": 9,
    "verse": 22,
    "text_sanskrit": "अनन्याश्चिन्तयन्तो मां ये जनाः पर्युपासते | तेषां नित्याभियुक्तानां योगक्षेमं वहाम्यहम् ||",
    "text_transliteration": "ananyāś cintayanto māṃ ye janāḥ paryupāsate | teṣāṃ nityābhiyuktānāṃ yoga kṣemaṃ vahāmy aham ||",
    "text_english": "Those who worship Me with exclusive devotion, thinking of nothing else, I provide for their sustenance and protection.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
  },
  {
    "parva_number": 6,
    "chapter": 9,
    "verse": 23,
    "text_sanskrit": "ये त्वेकं शुभांश्चैव मच्चिन्त्यान्यपि च | तेषां मनसां निगृह्य योगं करिष्यामि ||",
    "text_transliteration": "ye tvekaṃ śubhānś caiva mac cintyāny api ca | teṣāṃ manasāṃ nigṛhya yogaṃ kariṣyāmi ||",
    "text_english": "Those who think of Me exclusively and surrender all thoughts to Me, I discipline their minds in yoga.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
  },
  {
    "parva_number": 6,
    "chapter": 9,
    "verse": 24,
    "text_sanskrit": "अन्तःसुखाय संसारसागरमुपेक्ष्य | मामेव शरणं गच्छन्ति योक्त: ||",
    "text_transliteration": "antaḥ‑sukhāya saṃsāra‑sāgaram upekṣya | mām eva śaraṇaṃ gacchanti yoktaḥ ||",
    "text_english": "Forsaking the ocean of worldly existence for inner bliss, those who take refuge in Me attain liberation.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
  },
  {
    "parva_number": 6,
    "chapter": 9,
    "verse": 25,
    "text_sanskrit": "अनेकविधा भूतानि संन्यस्तकर्मवर्जिताः | भगवद्भक्तिपरायणाः ते मम प्रियतमाः ||",
    "text_transliteration": "anekavidhā bhūtāni sannyasta‑karma‑varjitāḥ | bhagavad‑bhakti‑parāyaṇāḥ te mama priyatamāḥ ||",
    "text_english": "Those who renounce diverse actions, devoted solely to Me, are very dear to Me.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
  },
  {
    "parva_number": 6,
    "chapter": 9,
    "verse": 26,
    "text_sanskrit": "पतयं मद्भक्तेभ्य: सर्वभूतानि प्रदास्यामि | उपासते हि मां भक्त्या सुखं लभन्ति चिरेण ||",
