    "text_english": "I give to My devotees all beings; those who worship Me with devotion attain happiness quickly.",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "chapter_name": "The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Secret",
    "chapter_name_sanskrit": "राजविद्याराजगुह्ययोग"
